div.p:
FOR which respect Anchrist is called (
   〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
) That Man of sin, by way of Eminencie or excesse therein, and v. 8. That lawlesse and wicked one, who as he professeth in his Cannon Law, (dist. 40 cap. 6. Si Papa &c.) Is to judge all but to be judged by none, altho hee should not only go to Hell himself, but also leade innumerable troups of People with him.
